{{Top|leg}}
'''Cynabar's Droid Datalog''' was a [[Scandoc/Legends|scandoc]] regarding [[Droid/Legends|droids]] and their usefulness to [[Smuggler/Legends|smugglers]], compiled by [[Cynabar]], notorious maintainer of [[Cynabar's InfoNet]]. Version 4.7.1 of the datalog was released on 37:8:1:47.

The datalog contained data collated from various [[NewsNet|newsnets]] and data archives, including secured files such as those of [[Galladinium Galactic Exports|Galladinium]]'s personnel manual and [[Imperial Defense Daily]] that had to be [[Slicer/Legends|sliced]] into to be accessed.

Comments from readers were appended to the entry on each droid, providing useful additional information and clarifications.

==Behind the scenes==
A significant portion of the roleplaying book ''[[Cynabar's Fantastic Technology: Droids]]'' maintains the in-universe conceit that it is Version 4.7.1 of this [[Datalog/Legends|datalog]].

